                <h3 class="lead">1. Eligibility</h3>
                <p class="colFooterText">Any individual who submits a fully complete application form for membership with a) address proof of residence / work b) mobile phone number &amp; proof of billing address and c) communicable email address is welcome to sign up with JustBooks Solutions Private Limited for the Company’s Library named JustBooksclc. However, JustBooksclc reserves the right to accept or reject membership at its sole discretion. Membership is for personal use only. However, it can be transferred to any other individual’s name with explicit communication to JustBooksclc. No member may re-lend books borrowed from JustBooksclc at any time. Doing so will entail automatic cancellation of membership.</p>
