                <p class="colFooterText">By subscribing to a specific membership plan of JustBooksclc, the member is explicitly agreeing to pay, in advance, the reading fee attached to the plan plus and any other applicable fee or tax at the frequency specified by the plan. Any non compliance with the payment terms in spite of 2 reminders will attract a penalty of 10% per payment period of the amount due and may lead to cancellation of membership.</p>
