                <p class="colFooterText">Since the reading fee is a flat rate and is not linked to the number of books read in a period, it is important to note that each title catalogued in JustBooksclc gets the same treatments irrespective of size, cost &amp; target reader. Children’s books are treated the same way as other books.</p>
